sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Gateway

    User            ->>  Gateway        :   HTTP GET http://server-gateway/api/v1/auth/verify/hasRole?=<<UserRole>> <br/>(with Access Token)
    Gateway         ->>  Gateway        :   verify signature with cached public key
    alt Unsuccessfull
        Gateway     -->> User           :   HTTP 401 Unauthorized
    else Successfull
        Gateway     ->>  Gateway        :   check token role
        alt Unsuccessfull
            Gateway -->> User           :   HTTP 401 Unauthorized
        else Successfull
            Gateway -->> User           :   HTTP 200 OK
        end
    end